[
  {
    "startTime": 0,
    "endTime": 3000,
    "duration": 3000,
    "text": "Imagine"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 9120,
    "endTime": 14080,
    "duration": 4960,
    "text": "you're a doctor and you're trying to"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 11440,
    "endTime": 17840,
    "duration": 6400,
    "text": "save the life of a patient, but you can"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 14080,
    "endTime": 20320,
    "duration": 6240,
    "text": "only see a fifth of their body."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 17840,
    "endTime": 22880,
    "duration": 5040,
    "text": "How are you going to prescribe medicine?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 20320,
    "endTime": 24800,
    "duration": 4480,
    "text": "How are you going to do surgery? See,"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 22880,
    "endTime": 28080,
    "duration": 5200,
    "text": "this is exactly the situation we're in"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 24800,
    "endTime": 30720,
    "duration": 5920,
    "text": "with nature across the planet. We need"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 28080,
    "endTime": 33360,
    "duration": 5280,
    "text": "to act now to protect ecosystems under"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 30720,
    "endTime": 36640,
    "duration": 5920,
    "text": "threat, but there's so much we don't"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 33360,
    "endTime": 39920,
    "duration": 6560,
    "text": "know about life on Earth."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 36640,
    "endTime": 42239,
    "duration": 5599,
    "text": "I'm an AI researcher and an ecologist."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 39920,
    "endTime": 44320,
    "duration": 4400,
    "text": "And as a professor at MIT, I lead a"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 42239,
    "endTime": 46480,
    "duration": 4241,
    "text": "research group that develops methods to"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 44320,
    "endTime": 49120,
    "duration": 4800,
    "text": "help us learn more about the natural"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 46480,
    "endTime": 51600,
    "duration": 5120,
    "text": "world. And I see a future where AI can"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 49120,
    "endTime": 54239,
    "duration": 5119,
    "text": "help exponentially increase our"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 51600,
    "endTime": 56320,
    "duration": 4720,
    "text": "ecological knowledge across species and"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 54239,
    "endTime": 58640,
    "duration": 4401,
    "text": "ecosystems."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 56320,
    "endTime": 61760,
    "duration": 5440,
    "text": "But to get there, we need to change how"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 58640,
    "endTime": 63520,
    "duration": 4880,
    "text": "we use AI in ecology. We need methods"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 61760,
    "endTime": 65760,
    "duration": 4000,
    "text": "that are flexible, methods that are"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 63520,
    "endTime": 68560,
    "duration": 5040,
    "text": "interactive, methods that scientists can"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 65760,
    "endTime": 70080,
    "duration": 4320,
    "text": "use to discover knowledge hidden in our"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 68560,
    "endTime": 72159,
    "duration": 3599,
    "text": "data."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 70080,
    "endTime": 73680,
    "duration": 3600,
    "text": "Now, let me tell you why this is so"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 72159,
    "endTime": 76159,
    "duration": 4000,
    "text": "important."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 73680,
    "endTime": 79040,
    "duration": 5360,
    "text": "Scientists estimate there are 10 million"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 76159,
    "endTime": 82400,
    "duration": 6241,
    "text": "species sharing the planet with us. But"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 79040,
    "endTime": 86000,
    "duration": 6960,
    "text": "we have only ever observed 2 million of"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 82400,
    "endTime": 87759,
    "duration": 5359,
    "text": "those. That means 8 million species. 80%"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 86000,
    "endTime": 90479,
    "duration": 4479,
    "text": "of the diversity of life on Earth"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 87759,
    "endTime": 93840,
    "duration": 6081,
    "text": "remains unknown."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 90479,
    "endTime": 96560,
    "duration": 6081,
    "text": "And we need to know much more than just"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 93840,
    "endTime": 99759,
    "duration": 5919,
    "text": "a species exists to be able to protect"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 96560,
    "endTime": 103040,
    "duration": 6480,
    "text": "it. Where does it live? What does it"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 99759,
    "endTime": 105439,
    "duration": 5680,
    "text": "eat? Does it migrate? How far? This"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 103040,
    "endTime": 108560,
    "duration": 5520,
    "text": "deeper knowledge about species takes far"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 105439,
    "endTime": 110880,
    "duration": 5441,
    "text": "more than a single observation. But it's"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 108560,
    "endTime": 112799,
    "duration": 4239,
    "text": "necessary to understand what puts"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 110880,
    "endTime": 115439,
    "duration": 4559,
    "text": "species at risk."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 112799,
    "endTime": 118479,
    "duration": 5680,
    "text": "So for an example,"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 115439,
    "endTime": 121119,
    "duration": 5680,
    "text": "what if insect populations crash across"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 118479,
    "endTime": 123759,
    "duration": 5280,
    "text": "North America? We know this is currently"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 121119,
    "endTime": 126240,
    "duration": 5121,
    "text": "happening. What does that mean for birds"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 123759,
    "endTime": 128080,
    "duration": 4321,
    "text": "that eat insects? Which birds are going"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 126240,
    "endTime": 129840,
    "duration": 3600,
    "text": "to be most at risk and which are going"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 128080,
    "endTime": 133200,
    "duration": 5120,
    "text": "to be able to adapt to other food"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 129840,
    "endTime": 135520,
    "duration": 5680,
    "text": "sources? What about predators further up"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 133200,
    "endTime": 137680,
    "duration": 4480,
    "text": "the food chain that eat birds?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 135520,
    "endTime": 139520,
    "duration": 4000,
    "text": "Everything is interconnected and a"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 137680,
    "endTime": 141760,
    "duration": 4080,
    "text": "threat to one species or a group of"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 139520,
    "endTime": 143840,
    "duration": 4320,
    "text": "species can ripple outward and trigger"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 141760,
    "endTime": 146080,
    "duration": 4320,
    "text": "the complete collapse of an ecosystem as"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 143840,
    "endTime": 148640,
    "duration": 4800,
    "text": "we know it."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 146080,
    "endTime": 151360,
    "duration": 5280,
    "text": "Unfortunately, species are under threat"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 148640,
    "endTime": 155120,
    "duration": 6480,
    "text": "from every direction. Habitats are"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 151360,
    "endTime": 159120,
    "duration": 7760,
    "text": "shrinking. Temperatures are rising."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 155120,
    "endTime": 161440,
    "duration": 6320,
    "text": "Food and water sources are disappearing."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 159120,
    "endTime": 164720,
    "duration": 5600,
    "text": "Natural disasters like fire are causing"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 161440,
    "endTime": 167360,
    "duration": 5920,
    "text": "large-scale death and displacement."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 164720,
    "endTime": 169040,
    "duration": 4320,
    "text": "and invasive species are moving in and"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 167360,
    "endTime": 170879,
    "duration": 3519,
    "text": "out competing native species for"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 169040,
    "endTime": 172800,
    "duration": 3760,
    "text": "resources."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 170879,
    "endTime": 175120,
    "duration": 4241,
    "text": "As a result, extinction rates are now a"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 172800,
    "endTime": 178000,
    "duration": 5200,
    "text": "hundred to a thousand times higher than"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 175120,
    "endTime": 180239,
    "duration": 5119,
    "text": "what we would expect based on past data."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 178000,
    "endTime": 182000,
    "duration": 4000,
    "text": "Scientists, policy makers, and community"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 180239,
    "endTime": 184959,
    "duration": 4720,
    "text": "members worldwide are racing to"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 182000,
    "endTime": 186080,
    "duration": 4080,
    "text": "understand what is causing this. What"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 184959,
    "endTime": 188159,
    "duration": 3200,
    "text": "are the factors that are most"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 186080,
    "endTime": 190480,
    "duration": 4400,
    "text": "contributing to this loss? And what"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 188159,
    "endTime": 193200,
    "duration": 5041,
    "text": "actions we can take to stop it. But"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 190480,
    "endTime": 195040,
    "duration": 4560,
    "text": "unfortunately, it can feel like we're"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 193200,
    "endTime": 197040,
    "duration": 3840,
    "text": "discovering species just in time to"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 195040,
    "endTime": 199920,
    "duration": 4880,
    "text": "write their obituaries."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 197040,
    "endTime": 202959,
    "duration": 5919,
    "text": "Take the topi orangutan. We discovered"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 199920,
    "endTime": 205040,
    "duration": 5120,
    "text": "this orangutan in 2017. It's one of only"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 202959,
    "endTime": 206800,
    "duration": 3841,
    "text": "three species of orangutan on Earth, and"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 205040,
    "endTime": 208879,
    "duration": 3839,
    "text": "it was critically endangered before we"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 206800,
    "endTime": 211040,
    "duration": 4240,
    "text": "even knew it existed."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 208879,
    "endTime": 213440,
    "duration": 4561,
    "text": "Traditional forms of data collection are"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 211040,
    "endTime": 215760,
    "duration": 4720,
    "text": "just too slow to keep up with our"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 213440,
    "endTime": 217920,
    "duration": 4480,
    "text": "current crisis. And this is where I"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 215760,
    "endTime": 221040,
    "duration": 5280,
    "text": "finally have some good news because we"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 217920,
    "endTime": 223920,
    "duration": 6000,
    "text": "are sitting on vast databases of"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 221040,
    "endTime": 227480,
    "duration": 6440,
    "text": "ecological knowledge and we have barely"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 223920,
    "endTime": 227480,
    "duration": 3560,
    "text": "scratched the surface."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 228000,
    "endTime": 231760,
    "duration": 3760,
    "text": "Let's talk about just one of these"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 229280,
    "endTime": 233360,
    "duration": 4080,
    "text": "databases which is a platform called I"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 231760,
    "endTime": 236080,
    "duration": 4320,
    "text": "naturalist."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 233360,
    "endTime": 239120,
    "duration": 5760,
    "text": "300 million images have been uploaded to"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 236080,
    "endTime": 241760,
    "duration": 5680,
    "text": "this platform by passionate volunteers."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 239120,
    "endTime": 244799,
    "duration": 5679,
    "text": "In every single image, the community has"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 241760,
    "endTime": 246879,
    "duration": 5119,
    "text": "identified a species. And that level of"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 244799,
    "endTime": 249760,
    "duration": 4961,
    "text": "species occurrence data has already been"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 246879,
    "endTime": 251920,
    "duration": 5041,
    "text": "transformative for science. But there is"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 249760,
    "endTime": 254879,
    "duration": 5119,
    "text": "a hidden treasure trove of knowledge"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 251920,
    "endTime": 257280,
    "duration": 5360,
    "text": "that remains in the pixels. So let's"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 254879,
    "endTime": 259359,
    "duration": 4480,
    "text": "look at just one of these images in I"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 257280,
    "endTime": 262400,
    "duration": 5120,
    "text": "naturalist. This was labeled Grant"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 259359,
    "endTime": 264639,
    "duration": 5280,
    "text": "Zebra. And it's clearly evidence that"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 262400,
    "endTime": 267360,
    "duration": 4960,
    "text": "Grant Zebra were cited in this place and"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 264639,
    "endTime": 269520,
    "duration": 4881,
    "text": "time. But it shows us so much more than"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 267360,
    "endTime": 271680,
    "duration": 4320,
    "text": "that. There are three grant zebra in"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 269520,
    "endTime": 273680,
    "duration": 4160,
    "text": "this image. We can identify each of them"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 271680,
    "endTime": 276240,
    "duration": 4560,
    "text": "to the individual level based on their"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 273680,
    "endTime": 278080,
    "duration": 4400,
    "text": "unique stripe pattern. By identifying"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 276240,
    "endTime": 280639,
    "duration": 4399,
    "text": "individuals, we can do things like"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 278080,
    "endTime": 283120,
    "duration": 5040,
    "text": "monitoring how species move across the"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 280639,
    "endTime": 285840,
    "duration": 5201,
    "text": "planet, looking at social networks of"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 283120,
    "endTime": 288639,
    "duration": 5519,
    "text": "species, growth, health, even estimating"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 285840,
    "endTime": 290720,
    "duration": 4880,
    "text": "the full population size. These zebra"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 288639,
    "endTime": 292720,
    "duration": 4081,
    "text": "are also coexisting with a herd of"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 290720,
    "endTime": 295040,
    "duration": 4320,
    "text": "wilderbeast. And if we look closely, we"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 292720,
    "endTime": 297440,
    "duration": 4720,
    "text": "can even see an oxpecker, a bird that"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 295040,
    "endTime": 299280,
    "duration": 4240,
    "text": "eats ticks and helps reduce the spread"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 297440,
    "endTime": 301120,
    "duration": 3680,
    "text": "of disease. We could look at the"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 299280,
    "endTime": 303840,
    "duration": 4560,
    "text": "background of the image and identify the"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 301120,
    "endTime": 306240,
    "duration": 5120,
    "text": "type and coverage of vegetation. We can"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 303840,
    "endTime": 308639,
    "duration": 4799,
    "text": "estimate biomass, use that to learn"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 306240,
    "endTime": 310479,
    "duration": 4239,
    "text": "about locally stored carbon. We can look"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 308639,
    "endTime": 312000,
    "duration": 3361,
    "text": "at what the animals are eating in the"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 310479,
    "endTime": 314160,
    "duration": 3681,
    "text": "image and build a stronger knowledge of"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 312000,
    "endTime": 316080,
    "duration": 4080,
    "text": "a local food chain."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 314160,
    "endTime": 318880,
    "duration": 4720,
    "text": "Take this much knowledge in one image"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 316080,
    "endTime": 321600,
    "duration": 5520,
    "text": "and multiply it by 300 million images in"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 318880,
    "endTime": 324400,
    "duration": 5520,
    "text": "I naturalist and then add in our other"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 321600,
    "endTime": 327039,
    "duration": 5439,
    "text": "ecological databases, millions of bio"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 324400,
    "endTime": 328800,
    "duration": 4400,
    "text": "acoustic recordings in Xenocanto, tens"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 327039,
    "endTime": 331440,
    "duration": 4401,
    "text": "of millions of camera trap images and"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 328800,
    "endTime": 333840,
    "duration": 5040,
    "text": "wildlife insights, thousands of hours of"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 331440,
    "endTime": 336400,
    "duration": 4960,
    "text": "deep sea footage in Fathom. We're"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 333840,
    "endTime": 338400,
    "duration": 4560,
    "text": "sitting on an ecological gold mine and"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 336400,
    "endTime": 340479,
    "duration": 4079,
    "text": "the problem is accessing the knowledge"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 338400,
    "endTime": 342479,
    "duration": 4079,
    "text": "efficiently."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 340479,
    "endTime": 344479,
    "duration": 4000,
    "text": "So say you want to look through all this"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 342479,
    "endTime": 346080,
    "duration": 3601,
    "text": "data. Assuming it takes you about a"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 344479,
    "endTime": 348800,
    "duration": 4321,
    "text": "second to look at every image, you would"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 346080,
    "endTime": 349840,
    "duration": 3760,
    "text": "need to work full time for 40 years to"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 348800,
    "endTime": 352720,
    "duration": 3920,
    "text": "look through all the images in I"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 349840,
    "endTime": 355039,
    "duration": 5199,
    "text": "naturalist alone. And this is where AI"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 352720,
    "endTime": 358720,
    "duration": 6000,
    "text": "is transformative. It can just help us"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 355039,
    "endTime": 361039,
    "duration": 6000,
    "text": "look through all the data quickly. So an"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 358720,
    "endTime": 363440,
    "duration": 4720,
    "text": "ecologist today say they're interested"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 361039,
    "endTime": 365440,
    "duration": 4401,
    "text": "in bird diets and they want to find"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 363440,
    "endTime": 367600,
    "duration": 4160,
    "text": "examples of birds eating insects in the"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 365440,
    "endTime": 370639,
    "duration": 5199,
    "text": "database. What they can do is they can"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 367600,
    "endTime": 372400,
    "duration": 4800,
    "text": "train an AI model to help them. So to do"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 370639,
    "endTime": 374639,
    "duration": 4000,
    "text": "this, they collect hundreds or even"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 372400,
    "endTime": 377280,
    "duration": 4880,
    "text": "thousands of examples to teach the model"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 374639,
    "endTime": 379520,
    "duration": 4881,
    "text": "what to look for. Now once they've"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 377280,
    "endTime": 382240,
    "duration": 4960,
    "text": "trained this model, it's an incredible"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 379520,
    "endTime": 384319,
    "duration": 4799,
    "text": "tool. It can very very quickly find new"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 382240,
    "endTime": 387520,
    "duration": 5280,
    "text": "examples of birds eating insects in the"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 384319,
    "endTime": 389840,
    "duration": 5521,
    "text": "database. But this process of collecting"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 387520,
    "endTime": 392240,
    "duration": 4720,
    "text": "hundreds or thousands of examples every"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 389840,
    "endTime": 394800,
    "duration": 4960,
    "text": "time we want to look for something new,"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 392240,
    "endTime": 396960,
    "duration": 4720,
    "text": "it's still too slow. So let's reframe"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 394800,
    "endTime": 400080,
    "duration": 5280,
    "text": "the question."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 396960,
    "endTime": 403280,
    "duration": 6320,
    "text": "Scientific discovery really begins with"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 400080,
    "endTime": 405199,
    "duration": 5119,
    "text": "scientific curiosity, with asking"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 403280,
    "endTime": 408560,
    "duration": 5280,
    "text": "questions about the world and how it"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 405199,
    "endTime": 410479,
    "duration": 5280,
    "text": "works. Things like, how far can a grant"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 408560,
    "endTime": 412479,
    "duration": 3919,
    "text": "zebra migrate?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 410479,
    "endTime": 414080,
    "duration": 3601,
    "text": "What plants grow back after a forest"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 412479,
    "endTime": 416800,
    "duration": 4321,
    "text": "fire?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 414080,
    "endTime": 418560,
    "duration": 4480,
    "text": "Do birds eat insects during the winter?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 416800,
    "endTime": 421120,
    "duration": 4320,
    "text": "Wouldn't it be great if instead we could"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 418560,
    "endTime": 424720,
    "duration": 6160,
    "text": "just directly ask questions to our"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 421120,
    "endTime": 426639,
    "duration": 5519,
    "text": "databases and get answers back? This is"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 424720,
    "endTime": 428880,
    "duration": 4160,
    "text": "what my team at MIT has been working"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 426639,
    "endTime": 430880,
    "duration": 4241,
    "text": "towards. And we've developed a system"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 428880,
    "endTime": 433759,
    "duration": 4879,
    "text": "that we call inquire that helps"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 430880,
    "endTime": 436000,
    "duration": 5120,
    "text": "ecologists find answers in the data"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 433759,
    "endTime": 438160,
    "duration": 4401,
    "text": "without collecting any examples to teach"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 436000,
    "endTime": 441039,
    "duration": 5039,
    "text": "an AI model or needing to write any"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 438160,
    "endTime": 442639,
    "duration": 4479,
    "text": "lines of code. Now, under the hood, what"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 441039,
    "endTime": 444960,
    "duration": 3921,
    "text": "we're doing is we're developing AI"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 442639,
    "endTime": 447440,
    "duration": 4801,
    "text": "models that can learn and understand"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 444960,
    "endTime": 449759,
    "duration": 4799,
    "text": "similarities between images and"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 447440,
    "endTime": 452479,
    "duration": 5039,
    "text": "scientific language. And this is what"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 449759,
    "endTime": 455039,
    "duration": 5280,
    "text": "allows us to just ask. So, how does"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 452479,
    "endTime": 457280,
    "duration": 4801,
    "text": "inquire work? Well, first an ecologist"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 455039,
    "endTime": 459120,
    "duration": 4081,
    "text": "designs an experiment by taking a"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 457280,
    "endTime": 461360,
    "duration": 4080,
    "text": "scientific question and breaking it down"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 459120,
    "endTime": 463280,
    "duration": 4160,
    "text": "into a series of search terms that they"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 461360,
    "endTime": 465280,
    "duration": 3920,
    "text": "can use to discover data that they'll"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 463280,
    "endTime": 468240,
    "duration": 4960,
    "text": "analyze downstream. So, one of those"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 465280,
    "endTime": 470960,
    "duration": 5680,
    "text": "terms might be bird eating insect. Now,"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 468240,
    "endTime": 473440,
    "duration": 5200,
    "text": "what happens is inquire takes that"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 470960,
    "endTime": 476879,
    "duration": 5919,
    "text": "search and it directly compares it to"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 473440,
    "endTime": 479120,
    "duration": 5680,
    "text": "all 300 million images within seconds."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 476879,
    "endTime": 480720,
    "duration": 3841,
    "text": "It's engineered to do this both quickly"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 479120,
    "endTime": 482319,
    "duration": 3199,
    "text": "and efficiently, which is important"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 480720,
    "endTime": 485120,
    "duration": 4400,
    "text": "because it means the system is truly"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 482319,
    "endTime": 486800,
    "duration": 4481,
    "text": "interactive, but it also requires far"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 485120,
    "endTime": 489599,
    "duration": 4479,
    "text": "less computational power than a"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 486800,
    "endTime": 491520,
    "duration": 4720,
    "text": "generative AI approach like chat GBT."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 489599,
    "endTime": 493520,
    "duration": 3921,
    "text": "Now, once all of these images are sorted"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 491520,
    "endTime": 495840,
    "duration": 4320,
    "text": "based on their relevance to the query,"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 493520,
    "endTime": 497919,
    "duration": 4399,
    "text": "it's really easy for a scientist to just"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 495840,
    "endTime": 500160,
    "duration": 4320,
    "text": "focus their attention on the data that's"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 497919,
    "endTime": 503039,
    "duration": 5120,
    "text": "most likely to be relevant to them and"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 500160,
    "endTime": 505440,
    "duration": 5280,
    "text": "quickly verify the true matches. Now you"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 503039,
    "endTime": 507039,
    "duration": 4000,
    "text": "have human verified examples of data"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 505440,
    "endTime": 509680,
    "duration": 4240,
    "text": "that you can directly export and"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 507039,
    "endTime": 511680,
    "duration": 4641,
    "text": "analyze. One of our collaborators used"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 509680,
    "endTime": 513919,
    "duration": 4239,
    "text": "this system and they found thousands of"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 511680,
    "endTime": 516399,
    "duration": 4719,
    "text": "examples of birds eating insects but"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 513919,
    "endTime": 519200,
    "duration": 5281,
    "text": "also seeds, fruit, nuts, kerrion,"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 516399,
    "endTime": 521440,
    "duration": 5041,
    "text": "nectar, plants. And then they took that"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 519200,
    "endTime": 523599,
    "duration": 4399,
    "text": "data that they discovered quickly and"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 521440,
    "endTime": 526800,
    "duration": 5360,
    "text": "they analyzed differences in species"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 523599,
    "endTime": 528480,
    "duration": 4881,
    "text": "diets between summer and winter. Now"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 526800,
    "endTime": 530480,
    "duration": 3680,
    "text": "what they found was that yeah, some"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 528480,
    "endTime": 533279,
    "duration": 4799,
    "text": "birds do eat insects in the winter."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 530480,
    "endTime": 535120,
    "duration": 4640,
    "text": "American robins actually do, but far"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 533279,
    "endTime": 537279,
    "duration": 4000,
    "text": "less than they do in the summer. And"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 535120,
    "endTime": 539519,
    "duration": 4399,
    "text": "some species like American tree sparrow"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 537279,
    "endTime": 541600,
    "duration": 4321,
    "text": "that are incredibly dependent on insects"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 539519,
    "endTime": 544399,
    "duration": 4880,
    "text": "as a food source in the summer don't eat"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 541600,
    "endTime": 547120,
    "duration": 5520,
    "text": "them at all in the winter. This entire"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 544399,
    "endTime": 552240,
    "duration": 7841,
    "text": "process, question to answer, took them"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 547120,
    "endTime": 554880,
    "duration": 7760,
    "text": "about 3 hours. Another team spent 1,560"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 552240,
    "endTime": 557279,
    "duration": 5039,
    "text": "hours manually curating the data to do a"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 554880,
    "endTime": 559519,
    "duration": 4639,
    "text": "similar study. And when you compare the"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 557279,
    "endTime": 561920,
    "duration": 4641,
    "text": "results from Inquire to that study, you"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 559519,
    "endTime": 564560,
    "duration": 5041,
    "text": "see an almost perfect match. I think"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 561920,
    "endTime": 568160,
    "duration": 6240,
    "text": "this is so exciting, right? It it means"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 564560,
    "endTime": 571440,
    "duration": 6880,
    "text": "that that we can start quickly getting"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 568160,
    "endTime": 575360,
    "duration": 7200,
    "text": "access to all of this hidden knowledge."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 571440,
    "endTime": 577760,
    "duration": 6320,
    "text": "And really, I've been so inspired by the"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 575360,
    "endTime": 580160,
    "duration": 4800,
    "text": "the creativity of the scientists using"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 577760,
    "endTime": 582560,
    "duration": 4800,
    "text": "the system, all of the flexible ways"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 580160,
    "endTime": 585680,
    "duration": 5520,
    "text": "that people have explored many, many"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 582560,
    "endTime": 589040,
    "duration": 6480,
    "text": "different questions. things like looking"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 585680,
    "endTime": 591040,
    "duration": 5360,
    "text": "at how forests regenerate after fire or"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 589040,
    "endTime": 593360,
    "duration": 4320,
    "text": "discovering differences in species"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 591040,
    "endTime": 595920,
    "duration": 4880,
    "text": "mortality between urban and rural areas"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 593360,
    "endTime": 597600,
    "duration": 4240,
    "text": "or looking at how flowering events are"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 595920,
    "endTime": 600240,
    "duration": 4320,
    "text": "changing in relation to a changing"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 597600,
    "endTime": 602560,
    "duration": 4960,
    "text": "climate. The possibilities are truly"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 600240,
    "endTime": 605519,
    "duration": 5279,
    "text": "endless. And the fact that it's"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 602560,
    "endTime": 606959,
    "duration": 4399,
    "text": "open-ended means that any scientist can"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 605519,
    "endTime": 611440,
    "duration": 5921,
    "text": "ask the questions they are interested"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 606959,
    "endTime": 612880,
    "duration": 5921,
    "text": "in. Now, this is also just the beginning"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 611440,
    "endTime": 615440,
    "duration": 4000,
    "text": "because we've shown that we can do this"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 612880,
    "endTime": 617360,
    "duration": 4480,
    "text": "for images, but we can also imagine"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 615440,
    "endTime": 620800,
    "duration": 5360,
    "text": "designing similar discoverydriven"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 617360,
    "endTime": 624399,
    "duration": 7039,
    "text": "systems for bio acoustic recordings, for"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 620800,
    "endTime": 626480,
    "duration": 5680,
    "text": "aerial video, for satellite data, for"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 624399,
    "endTime": 628560,
    "duration": 4161,
    "text": "GPS trajectories coming from animal"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 626480,
    "endTime": 631360,
    "duration": 4880,
    "text": "collars, any ecological data type you"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 628560,
    "endTime": 633120,
    "duration": 4560,
    "text": "can think of. And that brings up a whole"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 631360,
    "endTime": 635600,
    "duration": 4240,
    "text": "new opportunity because all of these"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 633120,
    "endTime": 637120,
    "duration": 4000,
    "text": "types of data are innately interrelated."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 635600,
    "endTime": 639360,
    "duration": 3760,
    "text": "They're all looking at the same thing."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 637120,
    "endTime": 642000,
    "duration": 4880,
    "text": "They're capturing complimentary but"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 639360,
    "endTime": 643760,
    "duration": 4400,
    "text": "distinct perspectives of life on Earth."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 642000,
    "endTime": 645760,
    "duration": 3760,
    "text": "And I can imagine a future where we have"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 643760,
    "endTime": 647680,
    "duration": 3920,
    "text": "systems that help scientists quickly"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 645760,
    "endTime": 649279,
    "duration": 3519,
    "text": "discover hidden connections between them"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 647680,
    "endTime": 653519,
    "duration": 5839,
    "text": "all."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 649279,
    "endTime": 656160,
    "duration": 6881,
    "text": "Now, of course, this alone cannot solve"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 653519,
    "endTime": 658480,
    "duration": 4961,
    "text": "our global nature crisis. But what it"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 656160,
    "endTime": 661040,
    "duration": 4880,
    "text": "does do is it helps us maximize the"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 658480,
    "endTime": 663519,
    "duration": 5039,
    "text": "value of data that we've already"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 661040,
    "endTime": 666480,
    "duration": 5440,
    "text": "collected. And that means that then then"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 663519,
    "endTime": 668640,
    "duration": 5121,
    "text": "in turn we can carefully understand what"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 666480,
    "endTime": 671120,
    "duration": 4640,
    "text": "knowledge gaps remain and strategically"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 668640,
    "endTime": 673519,
    "duration": 4879,
    "text": "use our resources to collect new data to"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 671120,
    "endTime": 676320,
    "duration": 5200,
    "text": "fill those. Overall, this means we're"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 673519,
    "endTime": 678079,
    "duration": 4560,
    "text": "reducing the time and the cost of"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 676320,
    "endTime": 681040,
    "duration": 4720,
    "text": "driving information that supports"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 678079,
    "endTime": 683440,
    "duration": 5361,
    "text": "conservation actions. things like"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 681040,
    "endTime": 685440,
    "duration": 4400,
    "text": "understanding how to ensure that food"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 683440,
    "endTime": 687360,
    "duration": 3920,
    "text": "and habitat resources are available to"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 685440,
    "endTime": 688959,
    "duration": 3519,
    "text": "species when they need them most, when"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 687360,
    "endTime": 691040,
    "duration": 3680,
    "text": "they're migrating through an area, when"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 688959,
    "endTime": 692399,
    "duration": 3440,
    "text": "they're breeding or rearing young, or"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 691040,
    "endTime": 695440,
    "duration": 4400,
    "text": "when they're recovering from natural"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 692399,
    "endTime": 698640,
    "duration": 6241,
    "text": "disasters like fire."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 695440,
    "endTime": 700240,
    "duration": 4800,
    "text": "We stand at a unique point in history."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 698640,
    "endTime": 702640,
    "duration": 4000,
    "text": "We have both an unprecedented"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 700240,
    "endTime": 705600,
    "duration": 5360,
    "text": "biodiversity crisis, but we also have"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 702640,
    "endTime": 708000,
    "duration": 5360,
    "text": "unprecedented tools to address it. We"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 705600,
    "endTime": 709839,
    "duration": 4239,
    "text": "have millions of people around the world"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 708000,
    "endTime": 712480,
    "duration": 4480,
    "text": "eager to contribute to nature"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 709839,
    "endTime": 714959,
    "duration": 5120,
    "text": "conservation and scientific discovery."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 712480,
    "endTime": 716880,
    "duration": 4400,
    "text": "And we have AI tools that enable"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 714959,
    "endTime": 719519,
    "duration": 4560,
    "text": "scientists to find patterns in all of"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 716880,
    "endTime": 721600,
    "duration": 4720,
    "text": "that data at scales impossible for"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 719519,
    "endTime": 723600,
    "duration": 4081,
    "text": "humans alone."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 721600,
    "endTime": 726959,
    "duration": 5359,
    "text": "The future of conservation doesn't just"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 723600,
    "endTime": 729440,
    "duration": 5840,
    "text": "lie in remote rainforests or deep ocean"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 726959,
    "endTime": 732320,
    "duration": 5361,
    "text": "trenches. The future of conservation is"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 729440,
    "endTime": 734560,
    "duration": 5120,
    "text": "hiding in our ecological databases. both"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 732320,
    "endTime": 737839,
    "duration": 5519,
    "text": "the ones we have now but also the ones"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 734560,
    "endTime": 740160,
    "duration": 5600,
    "text": "we have yet to collect and that is where"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 737839,
    "endTime": 743200,
    "duration": 5361,
    "text": "all of you come in because everyone can"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 740160,
    "endTime": 746399,
    "duration": 6239,
    "text": "contribute everyone can collect data and"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 743200,
    "endTime": 748880,
    "duration": 5680,
    "text": "upload it to platforms like I naturalist"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 746399,
    "endTime": 751440,
    "duration": 5041,
    "text": "every photo uploaded every sound"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 748880,
    "endTime": 754639,
    "duration": 5759,
    "text": "recorded every observation shared is a"
  },
  {
